#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Random_Number_Generation/randint.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Random_Number_Generation/randint.md:4
msgid ""
"简介：给定 1 个 seed 标量和 1 个 offset 块，返回 1 个 int32 类型的随机块。\n"
"原型：\n"
msgstr ""
"Description: Given 1 seed scalar and 1 offset block, returns a random block of type int32.  \n"
"Prototype:\n"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Random_Number_Generation/randint.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.randint(\n"
" seed,\n"
" offset,\n"
" n_rounds: constexpr = 10\n"
")\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Random_Number_Generation/randint.md:8
msgid "如果需要多个随机数流，使用 randint4x 可能比连续调用 4 次 randint 更快。"
msgstr "If multiple streams of random numbers are needed, using `randint4x` may be faster than calling `randint` four times in succession."

